City: berlin, prague
1. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the art-deco house is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
3. the egyptian is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |
| Food          | pepper    | avocado      |
| Hobby         | writing   | baking       |
| House   | victorian | art-deco |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | colombian    |
